    "notes": [
      {
        "componentKey": "n1",
        "kind": "technique",
        "stepKey": "s4",
        "text": "Powdered peanut butter carries real PB flavor and protein with a fraction of the fat of more spread - it's what keeps this a peanut-butter bar without the calories running away. The 30 g of real peanut butter is there for the richness and fudge that powdered alone can't give."
      },
      {
        "componentKey": "n2",
        "kind": "note",
        "stepKey": "s3",
        "text": "Brown sugar + peanut butter is the peanut-butter-cookie backbone, and the salt is pushed up for a salted-PB read. Want a PB-butterscotch spin? Add ~20 g butterscotch SF pudding with the dry ingredients."
      },
      {
        "componentKey": "n3",
        "kind": "pitfall",
        "stepKey": "s6",
        "text": "Underbake on purpose - peanut butter and whey both go dry-crumbly fast past done. Pull it looking a touch underdone in the center; it finishes setting as it cools."
      }
    ]
